Titolo: Moonglow Bay

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Moonglow Bay is a fishing role-playing video game developed by indie studio Bunnyhug and published by Coatsink. After being announced at the ID@Xbox event in March 2021 and the "Wholesome Direct" of E3 2021 on June 12th, the game was launched on October 26, 2021, on Microsoft Windows via Steam, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X; it was then released on the Epic Games Store on November 11th of that year. The player character, an accountant in their sixties, moves to a small town where they fish on a boat and cook dishes.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 71
